data.description: Nicely redone 3900 sq ft home conveniently located just steps from the #2 fairway at the Franklin County Country Club. Nestled on nearly 1.5 acres in a highly sought-after mature neighborhood, this property boasts a prime location for golf enthusiasts and plenty of room to spread out inside. 5 bedrooms (possibility for 6). 3 full baths, and closet space for days. Downstairs you'll see a modern kitchen with stainless appliances and granite countertops and spacious living areas accented by hardwood, solid plank tile and an abundance of natural light. The main level accommodates a master bedroom with a bath including double vanities and 4 additional bedrooms for family and guests. Mature trees keep front yard private while the backyard is expansive and to be enjoyed from the screened porch.
